  "intent_precise": "Protein Purification with Magnetic NI Resin: Using reservoir (reservoir, slot 1), magplate (plate, slot 3), deepplate (deep_well_plate, slot 4), e_plate (plate, slot 3). With magnetic module. (1) Mix 10 times at 150\u00b5L. (2) Incubate for 15 minutes. (3) Wait 1 seconds. (4) Pause: pmsg (5) Mix 5 times at 20\u00b5L. (6) Transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination. (7) Mix 5 times at 110\u00b5L. (8) Mix 5 times at 110\u00b5L. (9) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (10) Incubate for 3 minutes. (11) Disengage magnets to release beads. (12) Mix 3 times at 90\u00b5L. (13) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (14) Wait 1 seconds. (15) Pause: Please add tips to slots 8/9; plates to remaining slots (16) Disengage magnets to release beads. (17) Mix 3 times at 90\u00b5L. (18) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (19) Incubate for 3 minutes. (20) Disengage magnets to release beads. (21) Mix 5 times at 45\u00b5L. (22) Engage magnets at magheightmm height for bead separation. (23) Incubate for 3 minutes.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform magnetic bead separation. (volumes 20\u00b5L-150\u00b5L, ~26 min total)",
  "intent": "For this protein purification with magnetic NI resin, you'll be working with the reservoir in slot 1, the magnetic plate in slot 3, and the deep well plate in slot 4. Start by mixing 10 times at 150\u00b5L, then incubate for 15 minutes before pausing for the system message. Next, do 5 mixes at 20\u00b5L, transfer 20\u00b5L from source to destination, then perform two rounds of 5 mixes at 110\u00b5L each. Engage the magnets at the specified height for 3 minutes to separate beads, disengage, then cycle through the magnetic separation process with 3 mixes at 90\u00b5L (pausing to add tips to slots 8/9 and plates to remaining slots), repeating the engage/disengage sequence twice more before finishing with 5 mixes at 45\u00b5L and a final 3-minute magnetic separation.",
